&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.trumpf.com/filestorage/TRUMPF_Master/Corporate/Newsroom/Press_releases/2022_23/Corporate/221027-PR-TRUMPF-FiscalYear-2021-22/20221027-PR-TRUMPF-Fiscal-Year-2021-22.pdf&#34;&gt;https://www.trumpf.com/filestorage/TRUMPF_Master/Corporate/Newsroom/Press_releases/2022_23/Corporate/221027-PR-TRUMPF-FiscalYear-2021-22/20221027-PR-TRUMPF-Fiscal-Year-2021-22.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
